        content: `In the Govee Home app, tap your device to open the control panel. Use the color wheel to choose a specific color, or use the brightness slider to adjust intensity. The "Scenes" tab offers preset lighting modes — Sunrise, Sunset, Campfire, Ocean Wave, and many others — that cycle through multiple colors automatically. Tap any scene to preview it and tap the heart icon to save your favorites for quick access. You can also create custom scenes by programming a sequence of colors.`,
